        <item>
            <title>notification on ssh session</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 09 Mar 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <link>https://yneth.github.io/blog/notification-on-ssh-login/</link>
            <guid>https://yneth.github.io/blog/notification-on-ssh-login/</guid>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;Before executing script make sure &lt;code&gt;&#x2F;etc&#x2F;profile&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; runs scripts from &lt;code&gt;&#x2F;etc&#x2F;profile.d&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; and
do not forget to replace all required variables for telegram API.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre style=&quot;background-color:#f5f5f5;color:#1f1f1f;&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;cat &amp;lt;&amp;lt;EOF &amp;gt; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;profile.d&#x2F;ssh_notif.sh
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;#!&#x2F;bin&#x2F;sh
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;caller=&amp;quot;\$(ps -o comm= \$PPID)&amp;quot;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;if [ &amp;quot;sshd&amp;quot; = &amp;quot;\$caller&amp;quot; ]; then
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  BOT_TOKEN=&amp;#39;&amp;lt;YOUR_TOKEN_HERE&amp;gt;&amp;#39;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  CHAT_ID=&amp;#39;&amp;lt;YOUR_CHAT_ID_HERE&amp;gt;&amp;#39;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  MESSAGE=&amp;#39;login&amp;#39;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  curl &amp;quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;api.telegram.org&#x2F;bot\$BOT_TOKEN&#x2F;sendMessage&amp;quot; \
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    -H &amp;#39;Content-Type: application&#x2F;json&amp;#39; \
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    -d &amp;quot;{&amp;quot;\&amp;quot;&amp;quot;chat_id&amp;quot;\&amp;quot;&amp;quot;: \$CHAT_ID, &amp;quot;\&amp;quot;&amp;quot;text&amp;quot;\&amp;quot;&amp;quot;: &amp;quot;\&amp;quot;&amp;quot;\$MESSAGE&amp;quot;\&amp;quot;&amp;quot;}&amp;quot; &amp;amp;&amp;gt; &#x2F;dev&#x2F;null &amp;amp;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;fi
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;EOF
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;chmod +x &#x2F;etc&#x2F;profile.d&#x2F;ssh_notif.sh
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
</description>
